    "description": "This structured report template is intended to provide a standardized reporting scheme for brachial plexus MRI findings. A \"checklist\" approach is encouraged to ensure that all clinically relevant findings are addressed. The segments of the brachial plexus are separated to facilitate a precise description of any multifocal lesions, although this is optional.",
